## Next Steps
*   **SRv6 Data Plane:** Chairs will coordinate with SPRING WG chairs before initiating an official adoption poll.
*   **Multi-Domain Framework:** Chairs will initiate an adoption poll on the mailing list.
*   **General:** Authors of newly adopted queuing drafts (N-Score, PIFO, Deadline, TQF) to address technical issues raised during adoption calls in their next revisions.